quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  19,76,"Allāhu yó sì ṣàlékún ìmọ̀nà fún àwọn tó mọ̀nà. Àwọn iṣẹ́ rere ẹlẹ́san gbére lóore jùlọ ní ẹ̀san, ó sì lóore jùlọ ní ibùdésí lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa rẹ."
  19,77,"Sọ fún mi nípa ẹni tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn āyah Wa, tí ó sì wí pé: “Dájúdájú wọn yóò fún mi ní dúkìá àti ọmọ!”"
  19,78,"Ṣé ó rí ìkọ̀kọ̀ ni tàbí ó rí àdéhùn kan gbà lọ́dọ̀ Àjọkẹ́-ayé?"
  20,58,"Dájúdájú a máa mú idán irú rẹ̀ wá bá ọ. Nítorí náà, mú àyè àdéhùn ìpàdé láààrin àwa àti ìwọ, tí àwa àti ìwọ kò sì níí yapa rẹ̀, (kí ó jẹ́) àyè kan tí kò níí fì sọ́dọ̀ igun méjèèjì.”"
  20,59,"(Ànábì Mūsā) sọ pé: “Àkókò ìpàdé yín ni ọjọ́ Ọ̀ṣọ́ (ìyẹn, ọjọ́ ọdún). Kí wọ́n sì kó àwọn ènìyàn jọ ní ìyálẹ̀ta.”"
  20,60,"Fir‘aon pẹ̀yìndà. Ó sì sa ète rẹ̀ jọ mọ́ra wọn. Lẹ́yìn náà, ó dé (síbẹ̀)."
  21,34,"A kò ṣe bíbẹ gbére fún abara kan ṣíwájú rẹ. Ǹjẹ́ tí o bá kú, àwọn sì ni olùṣegbére bí?{1}.",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ āyah kẹjọ.
  21,35,"Ẹ̀mí kọ̀ọ̀kan ló máa tọ́ ikú wò. A sì máa fi aburú àti rere ṣàdánwò fún yín. Ọ̀dọ̀ Wa sì ni wọn yóò da yín padà sí."
  21,36,"Nígbà tí àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ bá rí ọ, wọn kò sì níí kà ọ́ kún kiní kan bí kò ṣe oníyẹ̀yẹ́ pé: “Ṣé èyí ni ẹni tó ń sọ̀rọ̀ nípa àwọn ọlọ́hun yín?” Aláìgbàgbọ́ sì ni àwọn náà nípa ìrántí Àjọkẹ́-ayé."
  22,10,"Ìyẹn (rí bẹ́ẹ̀) nítorí ohun tí ọwọ́ rẹ̀ tì síwájú. Dájúdájú Allāhu kò níí ṣàbòsí sí àwọn ẹrúsìn Rẹ̀."
  22,11,"Ó tún wà nínú àwọn ènìyàn ẹni tó ń jọ́sìn fún Allāhu lórí ahọ́n. Tí rere bá ṣẹlẹ̀ sí i, ó máa fi ọkàn balẹ̀ (sínú ẹ̀sìn). Tí ìfòòró bá sì ṣẹlẹ̀ sí i, ó máa yíjú rẹ̀ padà kúrò nínú ẹ̀sìn. Ó ṣòfò láyé àti lọ́run. Ìyẹn sì ni òfò pọ́nńbélé."
  22,12,"Ó ń pè lẹ́yìn Allāhu ohun tí kò lè kó ìnira bá a, tí kò sì lè ṣe é ní oore; ìyẹn ni ìṣìnà tó jìnnà (sí ìmọ̀nà)."